what is Regression analysis? A technique for determining the statistical relationship between two or more variables where a change in a dependent variable is associated with, and depends on, a change in one or more independent variable. it used for forcast time serires modelling. Relationship Between RASG Driving ^^^^ number of accidents importants for using regression significant of relatationship (depedent = independebt variable)/ strenght and impact of muliple indepedent varibles on dependent variable. Regression == no of independent variabel/ shape of Regression line / Type of dependent variabel. Linear Regression establishes a relationship between dependent variable (Y) and one or more independent variables (X) using a best fit straight line (also known as regression line).
